The '''Keeper of the Tower''' was a title bestowed upon a selected royal official of the palace on [[Tammuz-an/Legends|Tammuz-an]]. Their responsibility was to act as guardian to the [[Tammuz-an royal scepter]]. One of their functions included presiding over a coronation ritual wherein the heir to the throne of Tammuz-an placed the royal scepter inside a preselected housing within the tower on the first [[Star/Legends|sun]] of the equinox.

==Behind the scenes==
The Keeper of the Tower was voiced by [[Len Carlson]] in "[[The New King]]."

